{"type":"message","id":"dd3a52e6","parentId":"141c1f75","timestamp":"2026-04-27T04:49:55.118Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在这两个也已经写进去了。\n\n这次我补上的就是你刚问的：\n\n- **遗忘曲线模拟**\n- **蒸馏压缩效果评估**\n\n新增文件：\n- `FORGETTING_CURVE.md`\n- `DISTILLATION_EVALUATION.md`\n\n联动更新：\n- `MEMORY_DISTILLATION.md`\n- `HEARTBEAT_DISTILLATION.md`\n- `GLOBAL.md`\n- `MEMORY.md`\n- `memory/2026-04-27.md`\n\n所以现在这套系统已经不只是“记住和归档”，而是开始具备：\n\n- 强化高价值记忆\n- 弱化低价值旧记忆\n- 检查长期记忆是否臃肿\n- 评估蒸馏后是不是更短、更准、更可复用\n- heartbeat 周期性做轻量复查\n\n你这句如果要最直接回答：\n\n**是，遗忘曲线模拟和蒸馏压缩效果，现在也已经写入升级了。**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06da932db866b0fd0169eeeaee7c58819393fc1586db8d52fe\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":3171,"output":229,"cacheRead":56832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60232,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777265387584,"responseId":"resp_06da932db866b0fd0169eeeaed602081938a85f8b6ffce8267"}}
