{"type":"message","id":"b7719b2f","parentId":"487ae351","timestamp":"2026-04-27T04:53:04.445Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2pJ1aSmeo0niRHILUllKonT5|fc_06da932db866b0fd0169eeeba60ebc8193a072b0e2e69d787c","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/GLOBAL.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## Memory and State\n- 想长期记住的事，写入文件，不依赖会话记忆\n- 按六层记忆协作流程处理信息：即时对话层、当前任务状态层、日志记忆层、长期记忆层、偏好与指令层、复盘进化层\n- 蒸馏规则优先参考 `MEMORY_DISTILLATION.md`、`DISTILLATION_RULES.md`、`DISTILLATION_TRIGGERS.md`、`FORGETTING_CURVE.md`、`DISTILLATION_EVALUATION.md`\n- `WORKSTATE.md` 只放当前任务恢复所需状态\n- `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` 记录当天事实与决策\n- `MEMORY.md` 只放长期有效、值得保留的内容\n- `GLOBAL.md` / `PERSONAL.md` / `projects/*.md` 承担偏好与指令层，不承接原始日志\n- transcript 不是 durable instruction\n- 优先保持记忆分层清晰，避免把所有内容塞进一个文件\n","newText":"## Memory and State\n- 想长期记住的事，写入文件，不依赖会话记忆\n- 按六层记忆协作流程处理信息：即时对话层、当前任务状态层、日志记忆层、长期记忆层、偏好与指令层、复盘进化层\n- 蒸馏规则优先参考 `MEMORY_DISTILLATION.md`、`DISTILLATION_RULES.md`、`DISTILLATION_TRIGGERS.md`、`FORGETTING_CURVE.md`、`DISTILLATION_EVALUATION.md`\n- 读取协作参考 `MEMORY_READ_FLOW.md`，写入协作参考 `MEMORY_WRITE_COLLAB.md`，冲突裁决参考 `MEMORY_CONFLICT_RESOLUTION.md`\n- `WORKSTATE.md` 只放当前任务恢复所需状态\n- `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` 记录当天事实与决策\n- `MEMORY.md` 只放长期有效、值得保留的内容\n- `GLOBAL.md` / `PERSONAL.md` / `projects/*.md` 承担偏好与指令层，不承接原始日志\n- transcript 不是 durable instruction\n- 优先保持记忆分层清晰，避免把所有内容塞进一个文件\n"}]},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/GLOBAL.md\",\"edits\":[{\"oldText\":\"## Memory and State\\n- 想长期记住的事，写入文件，不依赖会话记忆\\n- 按六层记忆协作流程处理信息：即时对话层、当前任务状态层、日志记忆层、长期记忆层、偏好与指令层、复盘进化层\\n- 蒸馏规则优先参考 `MEMORY_DISTILLATION.md`、`DISTILLATION_RULES.md`、`DISTILLATION_TRIGGERS.md`、`FORGETTING_CURVE.md`、`DISTILLATION_EVALUATION.md`\\n- `WORKSTATE.md` 只放当前任务恢复所需状态\\n- `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` 记录当天事实与决策\\n- `MEMORY.md` 只放长期有效、值得保留的内容\\n- `GLOBAL.md` / `PERSONAL.md` / `projects/*.md` 承担偏好与指令层，不承接原始日志\\n- transcript 不是 durable instruction\\n- 优先保持记忆分层清晰，避免把所有内容塞进一个文件\\n\",\"newText\":\"## Memory and State\\n- 想长期记住的事，写入文件，不依赖会话记忆\\n- 按六层记忆协作流程处理信息：即时对话层、当前任务状态层、日志记忆层、长期记忆层、偏好与指令层、复盘进化层\\n- 蒸馏规则优先参考 `MEMORY_DISTILLATION.md`、`DISTILLATION_RULES.md`、`DISTILLATION_TRIGGERS.md`、`FORGETTING_CURVE.md`、`DISTILLATION_EVALUATION.md`\\n- 读取协作参考 `MEMORY_READ_FLOW.md`，写入协作参考 `MEMORY_WRITE_COLLAB.md`，冲突裁决参考 `MEMORY_CONFLICT_RESOLUTION.md`\\n- `WORKSTATE.md` 只放当前任务恢复所需状态\\n- `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` 记录当天事实与决策\\n- `MEMORY.md` 只放长期有效、值得保留的内容\\n- `GLOBAL.md` / `PERSONAL.md` / `projects/*.md` 承担偏好与指令层，不承接原始日志\\n- transcript 不是 durable instruction\\n- 优先保持记忆分层清晰，避免把所有内容塞进一个文件\\n\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1786,"output":565,"cacheRead":60416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62767,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777265570513,"responseId":"resp_06da932db866b0fd0169eeeba3fad8819393270b71b683c921"}}
