{"type":"message","id":"2c540275","parentId":"a42216f3","timestamp":"2026-04-27T04:56:51.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这张补的是读取侧最后一段关键机制，我已经写进去了。\n\n新增：\n- `MEMORY_RETRIEVAL_WEIGHTING.md`\n- `MEMORY_RETRIEVAL_GATES.md`\n\n联动更新：\n- `MEMORY_READ_FLOW.md`\n- `GLOBAL.md`\n- `MEMORY.md`\n- `memory/2026-04-27.md`\n\n现在读取协作不只是“先查哪层”，还多了两层判断：\n\n- **召回加权**\n  - 哪条记忆更该先被想起\n\n- **读取检票**\n  - 这条旧记忆该不该拿来指导当前任务\n\n也就是说，现在这套已经更完整了：\n\n- 写入有分层\n- 读取有路径\n- 召回有权重\n- 调用前有检票\n- 长期记忆有遗忘与强化\n- heartbeat 负责周期性提纯\n\n到这里，你前面发的那几张系统图，能明确落成规则文件的部分，我基本都补全到位了。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06da932db866b0fd0169eeec8f48408193acbed5f98764644c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":4754,"output":233,"cacheRead":62464,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67451,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777265800894,"responseId":"resp_06da932db866b0fd0169eeec8df2908193837197e8ad7f203c"}}
