{"type":"message","id":"fbfef75b","parentId":"86cfa14a","timestamp":"2026-04-27T04:57:11.616Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"升级了。\n\n这张图对应补进去的是：\n\n- `MEMORY_RETRIEVAL_WEIGHTING.md`\n- `MEMORY_RETRIEVAL_GATES.md`\n\n并且我还顺手把它接回了现有系统：\n\n- `MEMORY_READ_FLOW.md`\n- `GLOBAL.md`\n- `MEMORY.md`\n- `memory/2026-04-27.md`\n\n所以不是只“看过了”，而是已经实际落成规则了。\n\n这张图带来的核心升级就是两点：\n\n1. **记忆召回加权**\n   - 哪些记忆应该优先被调用\n\n2. **记忆调用检票**\n   - 某条旧记忆在当前任务里该不该放行使用\n\n所以答案是：\n\n**是，这张图的内容已经升级进系统了。**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06da932db866b0fd0169eeeca402208193b11c67e68f0eb84f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":33228,"output":181,"cacheRead":34304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67713,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777265823130,"responseId":"resp_06da932db866b0fd0169eeeca2bb208193b68bcf70d529a28a"}}
