{"type":"message","id":"f9ae337f","parentId":"00674399","timestamp":"2026-04-27T05:08:44.293Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6EBJX89xcqlN90PaOh4gcEQz|fc_06da932db866b0fd0169eeef5af9308193892ea51253a0c7c1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: gpt-image-generator\ndescription: Generate and edit images using a custom GPT responses API. Use when the user requests GPT-based image generation (text-to-image) or image editing (image-to-image).\n---\n\n# GPT Image Generator\n\nThis skill provides Python scripts to generate and edit images via a custom API endpoint.\n\n## Setup\n\nBefore using this skill, the user must configure the API URL and Key. An example configuration is provided in `references/env.example`.\n\nUsers should set these environment variables:\n- `PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_URL`\n- `PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_KEY`\n\n## Workflow\n\n### Text to Image\n\nGenerate an image from a prompt:\n\n```bash\npython3 skills/gpt-image-generator/scripts/generate_image.py \"your prompt here\"\n```\n\n### Image to Image (Edit)\n\nEdit an existing image based on a prompt:\n\n```bash\npython3 skills/gpt-image-generator/scripts/generate_image_edit.py --image <path-to-image> --prompt \"edit instructions\"\n```\n\n## Important Notes\n\n- The scripts save the generated image in the current working directory.\n- Always use the `message` tool to send the generated image back to the user immediately after success.\n- If editing, always pass the absolute path of the user's latest provided image to `--image`.\n- You can pass `--out-base <name>` to customize the output file prefix.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777266524136}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a89ceb8","parentId":"f9ae337f","timestamp":"2026-04-27T05:08:55.590Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我现在直接帮你跑，不再只回口头状态。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06da932db866b0fd0169eeef5f0ecc8193815a246323633d64\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_VKCbZEi3eea2L2TwnAcFmHGT|fc_06da932db866b0fd0169eeef5f8f708193929fe76b9beddf6c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"export PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_URL='http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1/responses' PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_KEY='[REDACTED]' && python3 /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/gpt-image-generator/scripts/generate_image.py \"一个电影般的奢华时尚大片场景设置在一座宏伟的复古图书馆内，拥有高耸的木质书架，柔软的薄雾覆盖着地板，发光的蝴蝶在空中漂浮。一位拥有短波浪波波头和柔和自然妆容的美丽年轻女子居中坐在一堆古董书上。她穿着一件优雅飘逸的香槟色缎面长裙，姿态优美，一只手托着脸颊。一个奢华设计师手提包醒目地摆放在前方。戏剧性的顶部聚光灯，对称构图，情绪化氛围，浅景深，超写实，高细节，8K，时尚杂志风格，高级美学，柔和阴影，丰富的色调。\"","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images","yieldMs":1000,"background":true,"timeout":600},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"export PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_URL='http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1/responses' PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_KEY='[REDACTED]' && python3 /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/gpt-image-generator/scripts/generate_image.py \\\"一个电影般的奢华时尚大片场景设置在一座宏伟的复古图书馆内，拥有高耸的木质书架，柔软的薄雾覆盖着地板，发光的蝴蝶在空中漂浮。一位拥有短波浪波波头和柔和自然妆容的美丽年轻女子居中坐在一堆古董书上。她穿着一件优雅飘逸的香槟色缎面长裙，姿态优美，一只手托着脸颊。一个奢华设计师手提包醒目地摆放在前方。戏剧性的顶部聚光灯，对称构图，情绪化氛围，浅景深，超写实，高细节，8K，时尚杂志风格，高级美学，柔和阴影，丰富的色调。\\\"\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images\",\"yieldMs\":1000,\"background\":true,\"timeout\":600}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":4541,"output":342,"cacheRead":64000,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68883,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777266524304,"responseId":"resp_06da932db866b0fd0169eeef5dc9388193bb837056720d41aa"}}
