{"type":"message","id":"463eeefc","parentId":"d3301492","timestamp":"2026-04-27T11:04:32.419Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，那先不接 Midjourney。\n\n你现在这套其实先把现有生图链路打稳更值，尤其是：\n- 提示词复用\n- 自动回传成图\n- 多图参考理解\n- 记忆蒸馏后的风格沉淀\n\n你后面想接别的，我再直接帮你落。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06da932db866b0fd0169ef42be94948193b16dc28348428ca2\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":73129,"output":83,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73212,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777287867294,"responseId":"resp_06da932db866b0fd0169ef42bd32a4819395d7ad8bf2ef465c"}}
