{"type":"message","id":"05bdeaf7","parentId":"b0cffc1e","timestamp":"2026-04-27T13:28:06.976Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，这一批高频 agent 我已经帮你优先注册进去了，而且这次是**真成功了一批**。\n\n新注册成功的重点包括：\n\n- `marketing-xiaohongshu-operator`\n- `marketing-douyin-strategist`\n- `marketing-wechat-operator`\n- `marketing-weixin-channels-strategist`\n- `marketing-bilibili-strategist`\n- `marketing-weibo-strategist`\n- `marketing-china-market-localization-strategist`\n- `marketing-content-creator`\n- `marketing-short-video-editing-coach`\n- `engineering-wechat-mini-program-developer`\n- `engineering-technical-writer`\n- `product-manager`\n- `project-management-project-shepherd`\n- `specialized-workflow-architect`\n\n另外这些本来就已经在，所以我跳过了：\n- `design-image-prompt-engineer`\n- `engineering-feishu-integration-developer`\n- `engineering-frontend-developer`\n- `engineering-backend-architect`\n- `engineering-devops-automator`\n- `engineering-ai-engineer`\n\n## 你现在可以怎么理解\n现在不是 211 个都完整注册了，但你**最容易马上用到的一批**已经能用了，尤其适合你现在的方向：\n\n- 小红书 / 抖音 / 微信 / 视频号 / B站 / 微博\n- 中国市场本地化\n- 内容创作\n- 短视频剪辑\n- 微信小程序\n- 产品管理\n- 工作流架构\n\n## 一个额外提示\n日志里还有两类提示，但不是这次注册失败的主因：\n\n- `Ollama could not be reached at http://127.0.0.1:11434`\n- `plugins.allow is empty ... openclaw-weixin ...`\n\n它们更像环境提示，不影响这批 agent 已经注册成功这件事。\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步可以继续帮你补第二批高频的，我建议优先这两个方向二选一：\n\n1. **marketing 长尾继续补全**\n   - 比如知乎、SEO、跨境、电商、播客、私域\n\n2. **engineering / support / testing 补强**\n   - 更适合做开发协作与自动化执行\n\n我建议先补 **marketing 长尾**，因为你刚装进去的那批和它们更连贯。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06da932db866b0fd0169ef645bb714819380ccd053d1409619\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":3840,"output":512,"cacheRead":111104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115456,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777296471453,"responseId":"resp_06da932db866b0fd0169ef645a47dc8193b9f093fe43ce5ec3"}}
