{"type":"message","id":"f1f07b50","parentId":"4d1589e1","timestamp":"2026-04-27T13:40:32.335Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"继续补成功了，这一批 marketing 长尾也已经注册进去。\n\n这次新增成功的包括：\n\n- `marketing-baidu-seo-specialist`\n- `marketing-zhihu-strategist`\n- `marketing-cross-border-ecommerce`\n- `marketing-china-ecommerce-operator`\n- `marketing-ecommerce-operator`\n- `marketing-private-domain-operator`\n- `marketing-livestream-commerce-coach`\n- `marketing-kuaishou-strategist`\n- `marketing-podcast-strategist`\n- `marketing-video-optimization-specialist`\n- `marketing-app-store-optimizer`\n- `marketing-seo-specialist`\n\n所以现在你在营销这条线上，已经有一批挺实用的中文 agent 了，尤其覆盖了：\n\n- 小红书\n- 抖音\n- 微信公众号\n- 视频号\n- B站\n- 微博\n- 知乎\n- 百度 SEO\n- 通用 SEO\n- 私域\n- 直播电商\n- 中国电商\n- 跨境电商\n- 播客\n- 视频优化\n- App Store 优化\n\n## 当前我对状态的判断\n你这套已经从“仓库文件装上了”推进到“核心高频 agent 真能调用了”。\n\n## 我建议下一步\n现在最值的是二选一：\n\n1. **继续补 marketing 剩余尾巴**\n   - 比如 LinkedIn、Twitter、Instagram、Reddit 这些出海向\n\n2. **切到 engineering / testing / support**\n   - 把开发协作、调试、测试、support 这条线补强\n\n### 我的建议\n如果你更偏当前实用性，我建议：\n**下一步切到 engineering / testing**\n因为 marketing 这一批已经够你立刻用了。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06da932db866b0fd0169ef6748f5988193a031516e181d161f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":10731,"output":384,"cacheRead":109568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120683,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777297221341,"responseId":"resp_06da932db866b0fd0169ef674776d881938417e41b9e8c5024"}}
