{"type":"message","id":"acffdfe8","parentId":"32ee3ae9","timestamp":"2026-04-27T14:19:36.471Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"目前补到这里了：\n\n## 已完成\n### 1. 仓库文件层\n`agency-agents-zh` 的 OpenClaw 工作区文件已经**全部落盘完成**\n- 总数：**211**\n- 位置：`~/.openclaw/agency-agents/`\n\n也就是资源包已经完整在你本机上了。\n\n---\n\n### 2. 已优先注册成功的一批 agent\n我已经把一批高频、你更可能马上用到的 agent 真正注册进 OpenClaw 了，主要有两类：\n\n#### 营销/内容方向\n- `marketing-xiaohongshu-operator`\n- `marketing-douyin-strategist`\n- `marketing-wechat-operator`\n- `marketing-weixin-channels-strategist`\n- `marketing-bilibili-strategist`\n- `marketing-weibo-strategist`\n- `marketing-china-market-localization-strategist`\n- `marketing-content-creator`\n- `marketing-short-video-editing-coach`\n- `marketing-baidu-seo-specialist`\n- `marketing-zhihu-strategist`\n- `marketing-cross-border-ecommerce`\n- `marketing-china-ecommerce-operator`\n- `marketing-ecommerce-operator`\n- `marketing-private-domain-operator`\n- `marketing-livestream-commerce-coach`\n- `marketing-kuaishou-strategist`\n- `marketing-podcast-strategist`\n- `marketing-video-optimization-specialist`\n- `marketing-app-store-optimizer`\n- `marketing-seo-specialist`\n\n#### 工程/产品/流程方向\n- `engineering-wechat-mini-program-developer`\n- `engineering-technical-writer`\n- `product-manager`\n- `project-management-project-shepherd`\n- `specialized-workflow-architect`\n\n另外一些工程类本来就已经在：\n- `engineering-ai-engineer`\n- `engineering-backend-architect`\n- `engineering-devops-automator`\n- `engineering-frontend-developer`\n- `engineering-feishu-integration-developer`\n\n---\n\n## 还没做完的\n### 3. 全量注册\n还**没有把 211 个全部注册进 OpenClaw**\n原因不是文件没装，而是：\n- `openclaw agents add` 批量跑太慢\n- 大批量时容易超时 / 被系统终止\n\n所以我现在采取的是：\n- **文件全装**\n- **高频 agent 优先注册**\n- **剩余部分按批次慢慢补**\n\n---\n\n## 现在一句话总结\n**文件层已经全装完，注册层已经补完一批高频营销和部分工程 agent，还没全量注册。**\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以直接继续给你补：\n- **engineering / testing**\n或者\n- **support / finance / legal**\n\n我建议先补 **engineering / testing**。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06da932db866b0fd0169ef706cf69c8193af8e4ffcfd11cecb\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":2146,"output":610,"cacheRead":118784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121540,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777299554359,"responseId":"resp_06da932db866b0fd0169ef7066c6a4819392a68574722b2c04"}}
