{"type":"message","id":"c1b33e50","parentId":"372d1d8a","timestamp":"2026-04-27T14:31:10.203Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"已经开始补，而且这一批 **engineering / testing 已经注册成功**。\n\n这次补进去的有：\n\n### engineering\n- `engineering-sre`\n- `engineering-threat-detection-engineer`\n- `engineering-voice-ai-integration-engineer`\n\n### testing\n- `testing-accessibility-auditor`\n- `testing-api-tester`\n- `testing-performance-benchmarker`\n- `testing-reality-checker`\n- `testing-test-results-analyzer`\n- `testing-tool-evaluator`\n- `testing-workflow-optimizer`\n\n所以你现在这套不只是营销角色库了，已经开始有真正偏执行和验证的 agent 了。\n\n## 现在这套的能力已经很像一个可工作的组合\n你已经有：\n\n- **内容/平台侧**\n  - 小红书、抖音、微信、视频号、B站、微博、知乎、SEO、电商、私域、跨境\n\n- **工程侧**\n  - 前端、后端、DevOps、AI、Feishu、小程序、技术写作、SRE、威胁检测、语音 AI 集成\n\n- **测试侧**\n  - API 测试、性能基准、可访问性、结果分析、现实校验、工作流优化\n\n- **流程侧**\n  - 产品经理、项目 shepherd、workflow architect\n\n## 一个提醒\n日志里反复出现的：\n- `Ollama could not be reached`\n- `plugins.allow is empty`\n\n目前**没有阻止注册成功**，只是环境提示，不是这轮补装失败原因。\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步可以继续补：\n1. **support / legal / finance**\n2. **剩余 engineering 长尾**\n3. **剩余 testing / specialized**\n\n我建议下一步补 **support / legal / finance**，这样你这套会更完整。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06da932db866b0fd0169ef73240ae8819381822faf88ffd9fe\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1094,"output":393,"cacheRead":124416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125903,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777300255916,"responseId":"resp_06da932db866b0fd0169ef73222208819391c346b568fe5f5f"}}
