{"type":"message","id":"3f2b4007","parentId":"d9c0c6c3","timestamp":"2026-04-27T14:43:34.361Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这批也补成功了。\n\n## 新注册进去的 support / legal / finance\n### support\n- `support-support-responder`\n- `support-analytics-reporter`\n- `support-executive-summary-generator`\n- `support-infrastructure-maintainer`\n\n### legal\n- `legal-contract-reviewer`\n- `legal-policy-writer`\n- `legal-document-review`\n\n### finance\n- `finance-financial-analyst`\n- `finance-fpa-analyst`\n- `finance-tax-strategist`\n\n## 现在你的这套 agent 结构已经比较成体系了\n你现在已经不只是“装了一堆角色”，而是有几条能协作的线：\n\n- **营销内容线**\n- **工程开发线**\n- **测试验证线**\n- **support 支撑线**\n- **legal 合规线**\n- **finance 分析线**\n- **产品 / 项目 / workflow 编排线**\n\n## 当前我对整体状态的判断\n已经从“试装”进入“能实际挑 agent 干活”的阶段了。\n\n## 下一步如果继续补，我建议优先这两个方向之一\n1. **剩余 engineering 长尾**\n   - 比如技术写作之外的更多工程专长\n\n2. **specialized**\n   - 里面常常有更像“总参谋”“跨域架构”“MCP/流程”这类高杠杆 agent\n\n如果你要继续，我建议下一步补 **specialized**，因为它通常最适合你现在这种主控 + 多 agent 工作流。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06da932db866b0fd0169ef760fc4d8819381212bfc199effcb\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":14196,"output":333,"cacheRead":115712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130241,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777300995183,"responseId":"resp_06da932db866b0fd0169ef7605a540819391176c5d7e1d10ed"}}
