{"type":"message","id":"6cf2c609","parentId":"63247f20","timestamp":"2026-04-27T15:10:02.516Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"继续补成功了，`specialized` 这组也进来了一批很有用的。\n\n## 新注册成功的 specialized\n- `specialized-chief-of-staff`\n- `specialized-mcp-builder`\n- `specialized-meeting-assistant`\n- `specialized-risk-assessor`\n- `specialized-ai-policy-writer`\n- `specialized-developer-advocate`\n- `specialized-document-generator`\n- `specialized-pricing-optimizer`\n- `specialized-model-qa`\n\n另外：\n- `specialized-workflow-architect` 之前就已经在了，所以这次跳过了\n\n## 这批的意义挺大\n这批不是平台运营型角色，而是更偏：\n\n- 总参谋\n- 跨系统编排\n- MCP / 工具接入\n- 风险判断\n- 文档生成\n- 模型质量\n- 政策与规范\n- 开发者生态支持\n\n对你现在这种 **主控 + 多 agent 工作流** 很配。\n\n## 现在整体已经很像一个可用的 agent 兵种库了\n你已经有了几条核心线：\n\n- **marketing**\n- **engineering**\n- **testing**\n- **support**\n- **legal**\n- **finance**\n- **product / project-management**\n- **specialized**\n\n## 如果继续往下补\n我建议下一步优先级是：\n\n1. **剩余 engineering 长尾**\n2. **剩余 support / finance / legal**\n3. **剩余 specialized 长尾**\n4. **game / unity / unreal / roblox / xr 这些偏专项的最后再补**\n\n如果你要继续，我建议下一步补 **engineering 长尾**，把工程线彻底做厚。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06da932db866b0fd0169ef7c410d4c8193abc44f9044982cf4\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":12696,"output":373,"cacheRead":121856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134925,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777302588358,"responseId":"resp_06da932db866b0fd0169ef7c3f3d088193b9afce8a21844125"}}
