{"type":"message","id":"c71ee33f","parentId":"8c7a0a2d","timestamp":"2026-04-27T15:12:20.661Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-04-27 23:09:43 GMT+8] Exec completed (fresh-co, code 0) :: http://127.0.0.1:11434. attempted specialized-chief-of-staff skip specialized-workflow-architect attempted specialized-mcp-builder attempted specialized-meeting-assistant attempte…\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"openclaw-weixin:1777302728514-a11e32a2\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-27 23:12 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n继续，你全自动帮我补齐后面的"}],"timestamp":1777302740505}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd428741","parentId":"c71ee33f","timestamp":"2026-04-27T15:12:39.673Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我继续自动往后补，不再每一小批都停下来问你。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06da932db866b0fd0169ef7cdcbf9c819384666ed591d001e4\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_jnqMV9RPg46bb9AFEqRk9Xss|fc_06da932db866b0fd0169ef7cdd53848193adaea9e6d5550dc3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport subprocess, pathlib\nbase = pathlib.Path('/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agency-agents')\nbatches = [\n    [\n        'engineering-solidity-smart-contract-engineer',\n        'engineering-wechat-mini-program-developer',\n        'engineering-technical-writer',\n        'engineering-sre',\n        'engineering-threat-detection-engineer',\n        'engineering-voice-ai-integration-engineer',\n    ],\n    [\n        'specialized-cultural-intelligence-strategist',\n        'specialized-salesforce-architect',\n        'specialized-workflow-architect',\n        'specialized-chief-of-staff',\n        'specialized-document-generator',\n    ],\n    [\n        'support-finance-tracker',\n        'support-legal-compliance-checker',\n        'support-recruitment-specialist',\n        'support-supply-chain-strategist',\n    ],\n    [\n        'finance-financial-forecaster',\n        'finance-investment-researcher',\n        'finance-invoice-manager',\n        'finance-bookkeeper-controller',\n    ],\n    [\n        'legal-client-intake',\n        'legal-billing-time-tracking',\n    ],\n]\nout = subprocess.check_output(['openclaw','agents','list'], text=True, errors='ignore')\nregistered = set()\nfor line in out.splitlines():\n    s=line.strip()\n    if s.startswith('- '):\n        registered.add(s[2:].strip())\nfor batch in batches:\n    for name in batch:\n        if name in registered:\n            print('skip', name)\n            continue\n        ws = base / name\n        if not ws.exists():\n            print('missing_workspace', name)\n            continue\n        try:\n            subprocess.run(['openclaw','agents','add',name,'--workspace',str(ws),'--non-interactive'], check=False, timeout=90)\n            print('attempted', name)\n        except subprocess.TimeoutExpired:\n            print('timeout', name)\nPY","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","yieldMs":1000,"background":true,"timeout":3600},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nimport subprocess, pathlib\\nbase = pathlib.Path('/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agency-agents')\\nbatches = [\\n    [\\n        'engineering-solidity-smart-contract-engineer',\\n        'engineering-wechat-mini-program-developer',\\n        'engineering-technical-writer',\\n        'engineering-sre',\\n        'engineering-threat-detection-engineer',\\n        'engineering-voice-ai-integration-engineer',\\n    ],\\n    [\\n        'specialized-cultural-intelligence-strategist',\\n        'specialized-salesforce-architect',\\n        'specialized-workflow-architect',\\n        'specialized-chief-of-staff',\\n        'specialized-document-generator',\\n    ],\\n    [\\n        'support-finance-tracker',\\n        'support-legal-compliance-checker',\\n        'support-recruitment-specialist',\\n        'support-supply-chain-strategist',\\n    ],\\n    [\\n        'finance-financial-forecaster',\\n        'finance-investment-researcher',\\n        'finance-invoice-manager',\\n        'finance-bookkeeper-controller',\\n    ],\\n    [\\n        'legal-client-intake',\\n        'legal-billing-time-tracking',\\n    ],\\n]\\nout = subprocess.check_output(['openclaw','agents','list'], text=True, errors='ignore')\\nregistered = set()\\nfor line in out.splitlines():\\n    s=line.strip()\\n    if s.startswith('- '):\\n        registered.add(s[2:].strip())\\nfor batch in batches:\\n    for name in batch:\\n        if name in registered:\\n            print('skip', name)\\n            continue\\n        ws = base / name\\n        if not ws.exists():\\n            print('missing_workspace', name)\\n            continue\\n        try:\\n            subprocess.run(['openclaw','agents','add',name,'--workspace',str(ws),'--non-interactive'], check=False, timeout=90)\\n            print('attempted', name)\\n        except subprocess.TimeoutExpired:\\n            print('timeout', name)\\nPY\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":1000,\"background\":true,\"timeout\":3600}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":135073,"output":570,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135643,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777302740665,"responseId":"resp_06da932db866b0fd0169ef7cda657081939929db4fff62ba99"}}
