{"type":"message","id":"622fddac","parentId":"86747cfc","timestamp":"2026-04-27T15:25:21.311Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我已经继续自动补了一轮，后面这批也进去了。\n\n## 这轮新补成功的\n### engineering\n- `engineering-solidity-smart-contract-engineer`\n\n### specialized\n- `specialized-cultural-intelligence-strategist`\n- `specialized-salesforce-architect`\n\n### support\n- `support-finance-tracker`\n- `support-legal-compliance-checker`\n- `support-recruitment-specialist`\n- `support-supply-chain-strategist`\n\n### finance\n- `finance-financial-forecaster`\n- `finance-investment-researcher`\n- `finance-invoice-manager`\n- `finance-bookkeeper-controller`\n\n### legal\n- `legal-client-intake`\n- `legal-billing-time-tracking`\n\n同时我也自动跳过了已经在的：\n- `engineering-wechat-mini-program-developer`\n- `engineering-technical-writer`\n- `engineering-sre`\n- `engineering-threat-detection-engineer`\n- `engineering-voice-ai-integration-engineer`\n- `specialized-workflow-architect`\n- `specialized-chief-of-staff`\n- `specialized-document-generator`\n\n## 当前状态\n我已经不是“等你每次确认一下再做”，而是在按高价值顺序持续补齐。\n\n你这套现在已经越来越接近：\n\n- 内容运营\n- 工程研发\n- 测试验证\n- support 支撑\n- legal 合规\n- finance 分析\n- specialized 编排与横向协作\n\n都具备一批可直接调用的 agent。\n\n## 接下来我会怎么补\n如果你没改主意，我后续默认继续按这个顺序推进：\n\n1. 剩余 engineering 长尾\n2. 剩余 specialized\n3. 剩余 support / finance / legal\n4. 再看是否值得补 game / unity / unreal / xr 这些专项\n\n你现在如果不想管，我就按这个方向继续自动补。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06da932db866b0fd0169ef7fd92e3c8193af3bc59fee62a1bf\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":13288,"output":413,"cacheRead":126976,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140677,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777303508764,"responseId":"resp_06da932db866b0fd0169ef7fd702f88193a4f0195b3f4b5b7f"}}
